title: Let's Eat! (Eating ASMR)
description:
Welcome to episode 123 of Sleep and Relax ASMR! Today I'll be eating crispy Cape Cod potato chips, as well as washing it down with canned Diet Coke. Enjoy!

Visit our website: www.SleepandRelaxASMR.com to get updates and access to special promos on awesome brands!
